OL,3,CThe King appoints Jersey's 91st Bailiff
OL,5,FThe Deputy Bailiff, Robert MacRae KC,
OL,6,Fhas been appointed as Jersey's next
OL,7,FBailiff by His Majesty the King.
OL,9,FIt comes after Bailiff Sir Timothy Le
OL,10,FCocq announced his retirement in
OL,11,FOctober last year, confirming Mr
OL,12,FMacrae's appointment in the States
OL,13,FAssembly on Tuesday 22 April.
OL,15,FMr MacRae says he feels "deeply
OL,16,Fhonoured" to be appointed to serve as
OL,17,FBailiff of Jersey.
OL,19,FHe adds: "The ancient office of
OL,20,FBailiff has been at the heart of
OL,21,FIsland life for over 800 years.
