OL,3,CThe King appoints Jersey's 91st Bailiff
OL,5,F"In times of need, the Bailiff has
OL,6,Fdefended Jersey's rights and
OL,7,Fprivileges, and in times of
OL,8,Fcelebration and remembrance, the
OL,9,FBailiff has represented the people of
OL,10,FJersey both at home and overseas.
OL,12,F"I will do my best as presiding
OL,13,Fofficer of the States, Chief Justice
OL,14,Fof the Island and Jersey's civic head,
OL,15,Fto serve our community, as Sir Timothy
OL,16,FLe Cocq has done."
OL,18,FRobert MacRae was educated at Jersey's
OL,19,FLa Moye School, Victoria College Prep
OL,20,Fand Victoria College.
