OL,3,CThe King appoints Jersey's 91st Bailiff
OL,5,FMr MacRae will officially retire on
OL,6,FSunday 19 October 2025, with Mr MacRae
OL,7,Fdue to be sworn in on Friday 24
OL,8,FOctober.
OL,10,FOutgoing Bailiff, Sir Timothy Le Cocq,
OL,11,Fsays: "Mr MacRae has a proven track
OL,12,Frecord of service to Jersey, which I
OL,13,Fhave no doubt he will continue to the
OL,14,Fhighest standard during his time as
OL,15,FBailiff.
OL,17,F"I wish him every success."
OL,19,FWhat is the role of the Bailiff of
OL,20,FJersey?
